Dear Sir/ Madam,

This is the second time we have sent our complaint that Downseeker.com has been crawling and scraping all software database on our site Wareseeker.com. And all infringing URL we sent in the last report was pointed to their another website downloadtarget.com. 

We strongly confirmed that all software being published on our site Wareseeker.com has been edited by our editor team. We are the owner of the copyrighted materials including the software description, screenshots and download links on Wareseeker.com. We have found thousands of pages on their site which display our copyrighted content.

We request Google to disable all access to the Infringing Material.
Please inform us as soon as the access to the Infringement Materials is
disabled.
